#                    two Z^4 endpoint offsets relative to the supertile anchor
# STRIP[(clsL, clsR)]     : decoration strip edges along a supertile edge
# REL_PATH/SIDE0          : the e1 shape in the edge frame (exact Q(sqrt2))
